\c 8
\s Temberi inotsaurirwa Jehovha
\p
\v 1 Zvino Soromoni wakaunganidza vakuru VaIsraeri, navakuru vese vamarudzi, iwo machinda edzimba dzamadzibaba avana vaIsraeri, kuna mambo Soromoni paJerusarema, akakwidza areka yesungano yaJehovha, ibve paguta raDhavhidhi, iro Ziyoni.
\v 2 Varume vese VaIsraeri vakaungana kuna mambo Soromoni pamutambo pamwedzi weEtanimi, ndiwo mwedzi wechinomwe.
\v 3 Ipapo vakuru vese VaIsraeri vakauya, vapristi vakasimudza areka.
\v 4 Vakakwira neareka yaJehovha netende rokusangana, nemidziyo mitsvene yese yaiva muTende, vapristi naVaRevhi vakakwira nayo.
\v 5 Mambo Soromoni, neungano yese yaVaIsraeri yakange yaunganira kwaari, vakafamba naye pamberi peareka, vakabaira makwai nenzombe, zvakange zvisingagoni kurahwa kana kuverengwa nokuwanda kwazvo.
\v 6 Ipapo vapristi vakagadzika areka yesungano yaJehovha panzvimbo yayo, panzvimbo tsvene yeimba, panzvimbo tsvene-tsvene, ipo panyasi pamapapiro amakerubhi.
\v 7 Nokuti makerubhi akatandavadza mapapiro awo pamusoro penzvimbo yeareka, makerubhi akafukidza areka nezvibatiso zvayo nechokumusoro.
\v 8 Zvibatiso zvakange zvakareba; naizvozvo miromo yezvibatiso yakange ichionekwa kana munhu ari panzvimbo tsvene pamberi penzvimbo pangataura Jehovha; asi akange asingawonekwi nechokunze; achiripo kusvikira nhasi.
\v 9 Mukati meareka makange musisine chinhu, asi mahwendefa maviri amabwe, akange aiswamo naMozisi paHorebhu, nguva Jehovha yaakaita sungano nayo navana vaIsraeri pakubuda kwavo panyika.
\v 10 Zvino vapristi vakati vabuda panzvimbo tsvene, gore rikazadza imba yaJehovha,
\v 11 naizvozvo vapristi vakange vasingagoni kumira pabasa nokuda kwegore; nokuti kubwinya kwaJehovha kwakazadza imba yaJehovha.
\s Mashoko aSoromoni nokunyengetera kwake
\p
\v 12 Ipapo Soromoni akati: Jehovha wakati: Ndinoda kugara mukati merima guru.
\v 13 Zvirokwazvo, ndakakuvakirai imba pamungagara, nzvimbo mamungagara nokusingaperi.
\v 14 Zvino mambo akatendeudza chiso chake, akaropafadza ungano yese yaIsraeri, ungano yese yaIsraeri ikasimuka.
\v 15 Akati: Jehovha Mwari waIsraeri ngaakudzwe, iye wakataura nomuromo wake naDhavhidhi baba vangu, akazvizadzisa noruoko rwake, achiti:
\v 16 Kubva pazuva randakabudisa vanhu vangu VaIsraeri paEgipita, handina kutsaura guta rimwe pamarudzi ese aIsraeri, pavangandivakira imba, kuti zita rangu rigarepo; asi ndakatsaura Dhavhidhi abate vanhu vangu VaIsraeri.
\v 17 Zvino Dhavhidhi baba vangu vakange vachida kuvakira zita raJehovha Mwari waIsraeri imba.
\v 18 Asi Jehovha wakati kuna Dhavhidhi baba vangu: Wakaita zvakanaka, zvawakange uchida kuvakira zita rangu imba.
\v 19 Kunyange zvakadaro iwe haungavaki imba iyo, asi mwanakomana wako wauchabereka, ndiye uchavakira zita rangu imba.
\v 20 Zvino Jehovha wasimbisa shoko rake raakataura, nokuti ini ndamuka panzvimbo yaDhavhidhi baba vangu, ndikagara pachigaro choushe chaIsraeri, sezvakapikira Jehovha, ndikavakira zita raJehovha Mwari waIsraeri, imba.
\v 21 Imomo ndakagadzirira areka nzvimbo, imo munesungano yaJehovha, yaakaita namadzibaba edu panguva yaakavabudisa panyika yeEgipita.
\p
\v 22 Zvino Soromoni akamira pamberi pearitari yaJehovha, pamberi peungano yese yaIsraeri, akatambanudzira maoko ake kudenga,
\v 23 akati: Jehovha, Mwari waIsraeri, hakuna umwe Mwari wakafanana nemwi kudenga kumusoro kana panyika pasi; munorangarira sungano nenyasha kuvaranda venyu, vanofamba pamberi penyu nomoyo wavo wese.
\v 24 Imi makaitira muranda wenyu Dhavhidhi baba vangu, sezvamakamupikira; makataura nomuromo wenyu, mukazviita noruoko rwenyu, sezvazvakaita nhasi.
\v 25 Naizvozvo zvino, Jehovha Mwari waIsraeri, itirai muranda wenyu Dhavhidhi baba vangu sezvamakamupikira, muchiti: Haungashaiwi munhu uchagara pachigaro choushe chaIsraeri pamberi pangu, kana vana vako vakangwarira kufamba kwavo, vakafamba pamberi pangu, sezvawakafamba iwe pamberi pangu.
\v 26 Naizvozvo zvino, Mwari waIsraeri, ndinokumbira kuti shoko renyu riitike, iro ramakataura kumuranda wenyu Dhavhidhi baba vangu.
\v 27 Ko mukati Mwari ungagara panyika here? Tarira, denga nokudenga-denga hazvingamuringani; ndoda imba ino yandakavaka!
\v 28 Kunyange zvakadaro, ivai nehanya nomunyengetero womuranda wenyu, nokukumbira kwake, Jehovha Mwari wangu, munzwe kudanidzira nokunyengetera komuranda wenyu, kwaanonyengetera pamberi penyu nhasi;
\v 29 meso enyu arambe achirindira imba ino usiku namasikati, nzvimbo iyi yamakataura pamusoro payo, muchiti: Zita rangu richagarapo; inzwai munyengetero womuranda wenyu waanozonyengetera akatarira kunzvimbo ino.
\v 30 Inzwai kukumbira komuranda wenyu, nokwavanhu venyu VaIsraeri, kana vachizonyengetera vakatarira kunzvimbo ino; donzwai henyu iko kumatenga, kwamunogara; zvino kana mukanzwa, muvakanganwire henyu.
\p
\v 31 Kana munhu achinge atadzira waanogara naye, akapikiswa mhiko, akauya akapika pamberi pearitari yenyu mumba ino,
\v 32 inzwai iko kudenga, muite, mururamisire varanda venyu, mupe wakaipa mhosva, arobwe pamusoro pomufambiro wake; asi mururamisire wakarurama, apiwe zvakafanira kururama kwake.
\p
\v 33 Kana vanhu venyu VaIsraeri vachinge vakundwa navavengi vavo, nemhaka yokuti vakange vakutadzirai; kana vakadzokerazve kwamuri, vakatenda zita renyu, vakanyengetera kwamuri nokukumbira mumba ino;
\v 34 inzwai iko kudenga, mukanganwire zvivi zvavanhu venyu VaIsraeri, muvadzoserezve kunyika yamakapa madzibaba avo.
\p
\v 35 Kana denga richinge razarirwa, mvura ikasanaya nemhaka yokuti vakange vakutadzirai; kana vakanyengetera vakatarira kunzvimbo ino, vakatenda zita renyu, vakatendeuka pazvivi zvavo, nokuti munenge mavarova;
\v 36 inzwai iko kudenga, mukanganwire zvivi zvavaranda venyu, nezvevanhu venyu VaIsraeri, nokuti munovadzidzisa nzira yakanaka yavanofanira kufamba nayo; munise mvura panyika iyo yamakapa vanhu venyu kuti ive nhaka yavo.
\p
\v 37 Kana nzara ikavapo panyika, kana denda rikavapo, kana nyunje nokuvhuvha zvikavapo, nemhashu nehonye; kana vavengi vavo vakavakomba panyika ina maguta avo; kana nyatwa kana hosha ipi neipi ikavapo;
\v 38 kana munhu upi noupi, kana vanhu venyu vese VaIsraeri vakanyengetera kana kukumbira, umwe neumwe achiziva kutambudzika kuri pamoyo pake, akatambanudzira maoko ake kuimba ino;
\v 39 inzwai henyu iko kudenga kwamunogara, mukanganwire, muite, muripire umwe neumwe zvakafanira mufambiro wake wese, iye wamunoziva moyo wake; nokuti imi, imwi mega, ndimi munoziva moyo yavana vavanhu vese;
\v 40 kuti vakutyei mazuva ese oupenyu hwavo pachiso chenyika yamakapa madzibaba edu.
\p
\v 41 Zvino kana ari mutorwa, asati ari wavanhu venyu VaIsraeri, kana akabva kunyika iri kure nokuda kwezita renyu.
\v 42 Nokuti vachazonzwa mukurumbira wezita renyu guru, noworuoko rwenyu rune simba, noruoko rwenyu rwakatandavadzwa kana akauya akanyengetera akatarira kuimba ino;
\v 43 inzwai henyu iko kudenga kwamunogara, muitire mutorwa zvese sezvaanokumbira, kuti vanhu vese venyika vazive zita renyu, vakutyei, sezvinoita vanhu venyu VaIsraeri, vazive kuti imba ino yandakavaka yakatumidzwa zita renyu.
\p
\v 44 Kana vanhu venyu vakanorwa hondo navavengi vavo nenzira ipi neipi yamuchavatuma nayo, vakanyengetera kuna Jehovha vakatarira kuguta ramakatsaura, nokuimba yandakavakira zita renyu,
\v 45 inzwai henyu iko kudenga kunyengetera kwavo nokukumbira kwavo, muvaruramisire.
\v 46 Kana vakakutadzirai (nokuti hakuna munhu usingatadzi), mukavatsamwira, mukavakumikidza kuvavengi vavo, vakatapwa kunyika yavavengi vavo, kure kana pedo;
\v 47 kana vakazozvifunga kunyika kwavakatapirwa, vakadzokazve, vakakumbira kwamuri panyika yavatapi vavo, vachiti: Tatadza, taita zvakaipa, taita zvisakarurama;
\v 48 kana vakadzokerazve kwamuri nomoyo wavo wese, nomweya wavo wese, panyika yavavengi vavo vakavatapa; kana vakanyengetera kwamuri vakatarira kunyika yavo, yamakapa madzibaba avo, kuguta ramakatsaurirwa nokuimba yandakavakira zita renyu.
\v 49 Inzwai henyu kunyengetera kwavo nokukumbira kwavo iko kudenga kwamunogara, muvaruramisire;
\v 50 mu kanganwire vanhu venyu vakakutadzirai, nokudarika kwavo kwese, kwavakadarika nako kwamuri; muvawanise tsitsi kunavakavatapa, kuti vavanzwire nyasha.
\v 51 Nokuti ndivo vanhu venyu, nenhaka yenyu, yamakabudisa Egipita pakati pevira ramatare;
\v 52 meso enyu ngaawone kukumbira komuranda wenyu, nokukumbira kwavanhu venyu VaIsraeri, kuti muvanzwe pakuchema kwavo kwese kwamuri.
\v 53 Nokuti imwi Jehovha, makavatsaura kundudzi dzese dzenyika, vave nhaka yenyu, sezvamakataura nomuromo waMozisi muranda wenyu, nguva yamakabudisa madzibaba edu paEgipita.
\p
\v 54 Zvino Soromoni wakati apedza kunyengetera kuna Jehovha munyengetero uyu wese nokukumbira uku, akasimuka pamberi pearitari yaJehovha, paakange akafugama namabvi ake, maoko ake akatambanudzirwa kudenga.
\v 55 Akamira akaropafadza ungano yese yaIsraeri nenzwi guru, akati,
\v 56 Jehovha ngaakudzwe, wakapa vanhu vake kuzorora, sezvaakatipa zvese; hapana shoko rimwe pazvese zvakanaka zvaakatipikira rakakona, izvo zvaakatipikira nomuromo waMozisi muranda wake.
\v 57 Jehovha wedu ngaave nesu, sezvaaiva namadzibaba edu; ngaarege kutisiya, kana kutirasi a;
\v 58 kuti arerekese moyo yedu kwaari, tifambe panzira dzake dzese, tichengete mirairo yake, nezvaakatema, nezvaakatonga, izvo zvaakaraira madzibaba edu.
\v 59 Zvino mashoko awa andakakumbira nawo pamberi paJehovha, ngaagare pedo naJehovha Mwari wedu masikati nousiku, aruramisire muranda wake, navanhu vake VaIsraeri, panodikanwa napo zuva rimwe nerimwe;
\v 60 kuti vanhu vese venyika vazive kuti Jehovha ndiye Mwari, hakuna mumwe.
\v 61 Naizvozvo moyo yenyu ive yakarurama kwazvo kuna Jehovha Mwari wedu, mufambe pane zvaakatema, nokuchengeta mirairo yake, sezvamunoita nhasi.
\p
\v 62 Zvino mambo naVaIsraeri vese pamwe chete naye vakabaira zvibairo pamberi paJehovha.
\v 63 Soromoni akabaira zvipiriso zvokuyananisa, zvaakabaira Jehovha, nzombe dzine zvuru zvina makumi maviri nezviviri, namakwai ane zvuru zvine zana namakumi maviri. Naizvozvo mambo navana vaIsraeri vese vakatsaurira Jehovha imba iyo.
\v 64 Nomusi uyo mambo akatsaurawo nzvimbo yapakati yoruvazhe rwakange ruri pamberi peimba yaJehovha, nokuti ndipo paakabaira chipo chinopiswa, nechipo choupfu, namafuta ezvipiriso zvokuyananisa; nokuti aritari yendarira, yaiva pamberi paJehovha, yakange iri diki kwazvo, isingagoni kuringana chipo chinopiswa, nechipo choupfu, namafuta ezvipiriso zvokuyananisa.
\p
\v 65 Naizvozvo Soromoni akatamba mutambo nguva iyo yese, naVaIsraeri vese pamwe chete naye, vakaita ungano huru, kubva pavanopinda paHamati kusvikira parukova rweEgipita, pamberi paJehovha Mwari wedu, mazuva manomwe namazuva manomwezve ndiwo mazuva ane gumi namana.
\v 66 Pazuva rorusere akaendisa vanhu, ivo vakatenda mambo, vakaenda kumatende avo nemoyo yakange ichifara, ichifarira zvakanaka zvese zvakange zvaitirwa Dhavhidhi muranda wake naIsraeri vanhu vake naJehovha.
